`,i.jsx("strong",{children:"Brevo"}),`
`,'Newsletter subscriptions and the delivery of the 3-Minute Breath Reset are handled via Brevo (Sendinblue GmbH). The Brevo signup form is not loaded automatically; it loads only after you click the "Continue to sign up" button. Processed data may include your e-mail address and any voluntary information you provide (e.g. first name). The signup uses a double opt-in process: you will receive a confirmation e-mail and your subscription becomes active only after you confirm it. You may unsubscribe at any time using the link included in every e-mail. For more information, please refer to ',i.jsx("a",{href:"https://www.brevo.com/legal/privacypolicy/",target:"_blank",rel:"noopener noreferrer",className:_t,children:"Brevo's privacy policy"}),"."]})},{h:"8. Embedded Videos and Media (Vimeo)",b:i.jsxs(i.Fragment,{children:["Embedded Breath Reset video and audio content is provided via Vimeo (Vimeo.com, Inc.).",`

